<<widget "hitchike_5">>
	<<generate1>>
	It doesn't take long for a car to appear on the horizon. You extend your arm and stick your thumb upward. The driver notices you and pulls over. The window rolls down.
	<br><br>
	"Need a ride?" The driver, a <<person1>><<person>>, asks.
	<br><br>
	<<link [["Accept and say you're going to town (0:15)"|Farm Hitchhike Accept]]>><<pass 15>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [["Accept and say you're going to the farms (0:15)"|Farm Hitchhike Accept]]>><<pass 15>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
