	You stand at the side of the road, waiting for a car to pull up. Once you see a car approaching, you gesture for it to stop.
	The vehicle comes to a halt next to you. The <<person1>><<person>> in it rolls down <<his>> window to talk to you. "Hey, where do you need to go?"

